ARM: tegra: Add OF_DEV_AUXDATA for SLINK driver in board dt

Add OF_DEV_AUXDATA for slink driver for Tegra20 and Tegra30
board dt files.
Set the parent clock of slink controller to PLLP and configure
clock to 100MHz.

